import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { Title } from '@angular/platform-browser'; import { AuthenticationService } from 'src/app/core/service/auth.service'; @Component({ selector: 'app-logout', templateUrl: './logout.component.html', styleUrls: ['./logout.component.scss'] }) export class LogoutComponent implements OnInit { constructor (private authenticationService: AuthenticationService, private titleService: Title) { titleService.setTitle("Logout | Shreyu - Responsive Angular and Bootstrap 5 Admin Dashboard Template") } ngOnInit(): void { this.authenticationService.logout(); } }
